io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.data.provider

Interface BlockLootProviderBase.LootModifier

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BlockLootProviderBase.GenericLootModifier, BlockLootProviderBase.LootFactory, BlockLootProviderBase.StandaloneLootFactory
    Enclosing class:
    BlockLootProviderBase
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface BlockLootProviderBase.LootModifier
extends BlockLootProviderBase.GenericLootModifier, BlockLootProviderBase.StandaloneLootFactory
    Interface to modify a standalone loot entry to a new standalone loot entry. This can also be used as a BlockLootProviderBase.StandaloneLootFactory in which case the default item entry obtained from BlockLootProviderBase.StandaloneLootFactory.item() is passed to the apply method.
